channel.title: So what's this error mean? (about item drops)
channel.description:
So these NPC's were working fine, nazastarools or whatever.
I was making drops and edited some public static in LD() thing to make it for 'em and it drops waters, deaths, and ectos.
So, I checked the ID's all right..
It drops 200 of each, but sometimes when they die I like freeze up along with everyone else and the server crashes.
I get this error in RunServer:
